[root@topeet:~/chapter12/83_gpioctrl02]# ./gpioctrl 42
gpio_path:  /sys/class/gpio/gpio42
file_path:  /sys/class/gpio/gpio42/value
The value is low
The value is 0
[root@topeet:~/chapter12/83_gpioctrl02]# ./gpioctrl 42
gpio_path:  /sys/class/gpio/gpio42
file_path:  /sys/class/gpio/gpio42/value
The value is high
The value is 1
